Voice command is now added! 🎙️ Here's how to use it:

**Just tap the mic and say:**
- *"Surya Lohani part two"* → fills name + selects ii
- *"Ram Bahadur single"* → fills name + selects i
- *"Dhan Kumari triple"* → fills name + selects iii
- *"Bikesh double"* → fills name + selects ii

**It understands many ways to say the parts:**
- Single / one / 1 / part one → **i**
- Double / two / 2 / part two → **ii**
- Triple / three / 3 / part three → **iii**

After voice fills the name and part, just tap **ADD PATIENT** — done in seconds! 😊

> **Note:** Voice works on Chrome browser on Android. Make sure to allow microphone permission when asked.
